function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

	if sLevelAreaName == S_LEVELAREA_SELF then
		Hydra.EventSend("ActivateWindCheck")
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_NORMAL", idActorPlayer)

	-- remove sandstorm buffs and damage when you are no longer in the level area
	else
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_DEADLY", idActorPlayer)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", idActorPlayer)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", idActorPlayer)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_NORMAL", idActorPlayer)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_HIGH", idActorPlayer)
		
		local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_SELF)
		local nPlayersAlive = 0;

		for i, ActorID in ipairs(tPlayers) do

			if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(ActorID) then
				nPlayersAlive = nPlayersAlive + 1;
			end
			
		end

		if nPlayersAlive == 0 then
			Hydra.EventSend("ResetWinds")
		end
		
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_SELF)
	local nPlayersAlive = 0;

		end
		
	end

	end

end

function Start(flGameTime)

	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_SELF)
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		if not Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM_SAFE, "BUFF_SAFEZONE", ActorID) then 
		
			-- No Safezone, No High Damage. Cleanup any lingering damage effects and apply correct effect
	 		if not Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_HIGH", ActorID) then
				if Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", ActorID) then
					Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", ActorID)
				end	
				if not Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", ActorID) then
					Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", ActorID)
				end

			-- No Safezone, Yes high damage
			elseif Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_HIGH", ActorID) then
				if Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", ActorID) then
					Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", ActorID)
				end
				if not Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", ActorID) then
					Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", ActorID)
				end
			end
		-- yes safezone
		else
			Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE", ActorID)
			Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_HIGH", ActorID)
			Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "STORM_DAMAGE_DEADLY", ActorID)
		end
	end


end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)	
	
	HighWindsActive = true
	
	-- Start High Winds DoT for all party members
	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea("Kehj_Ridge")
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_HIGH", ActorID)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_NORMAL", ActorID)	
	end
	
	-- Spawn Tornados
	local S_SANDSTORM_TORNADO = Hydra.ReferenceActor("VGN_Kehj_EliasPalace_Sandstorm_Tornado_Invisible_Parent");
	local tTornados = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_EliasPalace_Tornado_Marker")
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tTornados) do
		CurrentTornado = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_SANDSTORM_TORNADO, ActorID)	
		Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(CurrentTornado, "QST_Kehj_EliasPalace_Tornado")
	end

end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)

	-- Time to Go Sound Que
	-- no longer possible to access the sandstorm before being on the quest
	
	local tParty = Hydra.PlayerActors()

	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tParty) do
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_HIGH", ActorID)
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_SANDSTORM, "SANDSTORM_VISUAL_NORMAL", ActorID)	
	end
	-- Remove any spawned tornados
	local tSpawnedTornados = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_EliasPalace_Tornado")
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tSpawnedTornados) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(ActorID)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- pulls the the player who entered the safe zone. this is used to play the exit hint dialogue
	idActorPlayer = idActor
	
end
